### Tested versions

Reproduced in 4.5.1

### System information

Windows 11 - Godot 4.5.1

### Issue description

Script configured in Project Settings -> Import Defaults is NOT called when importing blend files.

The same script IS called when configured in Import tab for individual blend file.

### Steps to reproduce

1. Write a script extends EditorScenePostImport and marked tool;
2. Override _post_import(scene) and print out some text in it;
3. Open Project Settings -> Import Defaults, select Importer dropdown to Scene;
4. Put script into Import Script Path field;
5. Click Save button and close Project Settings;
6. Modify a blend file or run re-import, no print in console;
7. Now you can put script in Import tab for the individual blend file;
8. Repeat step 6 and you will find printed text in console.

### Minimal reproduction project (MRP)

N/A
